# The `NN-next.md` placeholder inside CLAUDE.md's required-topic-file
# example is illustrative, not a real link — the surrounding block is
# a ```markdown code sample, not prose.
NN-next\.md

# Local build artifacts referenced from example READMEs (they are
# produced at build time and never committed).
examples/[0-9][0-9]-[a-z-]*/[a-z-]+$

# OSDev wiki rejects lychee's default user agent with 403. Content is
# live — verified in a browser — so the block is a UA-level rate limit,
# not a real dead link.
^https?://wiki\.osdev\.org/
